5292 /******************************************************************************/
5293 /* For a painless codes migration between the STM32F0xx device product */
5294 /* lines, the aliases defined below are put in place to overcome the */
5295 /* differences in the interrupt handlers and IRQn definitions. */
5296 /* No need to update developed interrupt code when moving across */
5297 /* product lines within the same STM32F0 Family */
5298 /******************************************************************************/
